56:34.057 --> 56:35.684
Quickly. Let's...

56:36.643 --> 56:38.145
Let's look again.

56:58.540 --> 57:00.884
Wait! Stay close to me.

57:03.921 --> 57:05.423
Give me your hand.

57:07.841 --> 57:09.514
It's okay.

57:12.346 --> 57:14.098
It's okay.

57:54.846 --> 57:56.519
What?

57:58.058 --> 58:00.060
That wasn't on before.

59:52.547 --> 59:54.220
They took him.

59:56.927 --> 59:59.601
