01:10:46.409 --> 01:10:48.753
That's not the key
to this door.

01:10:49.495 --> 01:10:51.372
That's not the way out.

01:11:32.705 --> 01:11:34.048
Daddy?

01:11:39.670 --> 01:11:41.217
What did you do to him?

01:11:41.297 --> 01:11:42.719
